title: Extend ITR filing due date, HC tells CBDT
description: The Punjab and Haryana High Court ordered CBDT to extend the ITR filing due date for audited assessees. The extension, due to delays in e-filing utilities and system changes, pushes the deadline to November 30, 2025, for the assessment year 2025-26.

title: International experts show interest in importing fruits, cut flowers from Bilaspur
description: A Dubai business delegation visited Himachal Pradesh to explore fruit and cut flower export opportunities. The HP SHIVA project produces high-quality crops meeting international standards through cluster-based farming, farmer training, and modern techniques. The delegation expressed interest in long-term export partnerships after inspecting the Karot cluster.
